  <original-body>The attached patch allow to pass options to namespace in routes, such as :path, as in the following example:

    namespace :customers, :path =&gt; 'clientes' do
      root :to =&gt; 'home#index'
    end

This is a really common situation in Rails 2.x apps, when the path might be different.</original-body>
